# Random
####

node_modules

# Vite writes these transient config bundles next to vite.config when (re)loading config
vite.config.*.timestamp-*

*.db

/stash
/Stash.app
/phasher
dist
.DS_Store
/.local*
.agent/workflows/upstream-sync.md
stash-go.sqlite
