stash-go.sqlite-wal
docs/# Meta Design Graphic Rendering Pipeline.md

# Premium, purchase-only add-on plugins (e.g. FapTap VR) — never committed to the
# main repo. The compiled Go route + baked-in VR code ship in the build; only the
# plugin manifest/settings surface lives here and is distributed separately.
/plugins/
